{"tid":523844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"控方指女童疑遭生父舉高　頭撞天花板逾10次","createTime":"2018-01-09T03:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T09:13:54.000Z","uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"85ac3efdff7ebefadbdf8ff2100b5a5dfcde229d","tid":523844,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/147882/-5歲女被虐殺案-控方指女童疑遭生父舉高-頭撞天花板逾10次\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F147882%2F-5%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E8%99%90%E6%AE%BA%E6%A1%88-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E7%94%9F%E7%88%B6%E8%88%89%E9%AB%98-%E9%A0%AD%E6%92%9E%E5%A4%A9%E8%8A%B1%E6%9D%BF%E9%80%BE10%E6%AC%A1&d=F015TIYXqsL6BEeyf7lUgZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=37e1209f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/147882/-5歲女被虐殺案-控方指女童疑遭生父舉高-頭撞天花板逾10次</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯門5歲女童「臨臨」陳瑞臨疑慘被親父繼母虐打致死，其生父繼母被控一項謀殺罪，案件今在屯門法院提堂。控方庭上透露，警方調查時不但發現有血跡證物，更在女童8歲兄長在口供得知，男被告曾把女童舉高，至女童的頭部撞天花板10多下，兩被告亦曾抓住女童的手腳左右搖晃。裁判官將案件押後至3月6日以供警方作進一步調查包括作科學鑑證及索取兒子的醫療報告及女童死因報告。"},{"pid":"47e56e567c0f3686842ff15660719363a5c02b84","tid":523844,"uid":8681,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"陪審團到時可能好快達成一致意見判呢兩條人渣MK"},{"pid":"356446c8cda8d2f264f31b72bcc1206dc36437b3","tid":523844,"uid":26768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:54:43.000Z","msg":"個哥哥一定好大陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c2cbfea7e07ec0e78c8d64dc26e757dc23c652","tid":523844,"uid":165875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb5d5b5df6a601be82d5c63cbf9c77248d0bc29","tid":523844,"uid":165875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"